  {
    numeral: 'I',
    tag: 'Docs & Playbooks',
    title: 'Knowledge at the Ready',
    description: 'Serve project docs to your AI precisely when needed. Phase-by-phase playbook delivery keeps context lean and prevents LLM overflow.',
